query:

  propertyId, name, relationship, phone1, phone2,
  createdAt, updatedAt
) VALUES (
  (SELECT id FROM properties WHERE addressLine1 = '1513 NW 24th Ave' AND city = 'Fort Lauderdale' ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1),
  'Billy Dale Williams',
  'Deceased Owner',
  '(954) 687-3030',
  '(954) 588-1121',
  NOW(),
  NOW()
);
